<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦很享受这个下午。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿童中心夏令营的孩子们走在树林里，观察大自然。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦喜欢树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师正在给他们看苔藓和各种野花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是毛茛花。” 尼娜说，“真可爱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们什么都不摸。” 邓恩老师严厉地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只在路上观察，伊坦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈，伊坦！” 波比嘲笑他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有麻烦了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，邓恩老师让大家画昨天看到的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伊坦，你的腿怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪指着伊坦腿上的小红点说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦一直在挠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。但是真的很痒。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糟了。看上去是毒藤。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也会被传染吗？” 贾森离伊坦远远的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，你不用担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦昨天离开了小路。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，老师。” 伊坦小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该跟大家一起走的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的皮肤碰到了毒藤的油。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“油？” 贾森说，“什么油？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“植物有油吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来我们要学一学毒藤的知识了。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先去图书馆吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以在那里找关于毒藤的知识。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们等会儿再继续画画。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师带着孩子们走进了图书馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在电脑上找！” 男生们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在书上找！” 莉琪和尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师打电话给伊坦的妈妈，告诉她关于伊坦的皮疹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他给伊坦一个冰袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>冰袋起了一点作用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小时后，孩子们聚在地毯上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁来说一下自己找到的内容？” 邓恩老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比举起手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我发现毒藤是一种带有油的植物，会引起皮疹。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“触摸植物或者触摸碰过植物的东西就会起皮疹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比如鞋子。” 波比说，“或者宠物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时，第二天才会起皮疹。” 贾森补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。皮疹一般是12到48个小时之后出现的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师说，“但并不是每一个人都这样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们找到了一些照片。” 尼娜拿起一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还找到了治疗方法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>涂止痒膏和炉甘石乳液，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>再用燕麦洗冷水澡。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森在急救箱里找了找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找到炉甘石乳液了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要涂这个粉色的东西吗？” 伊坦皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是毒藤的照片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我们看到它时，要避开它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪给大家看照片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有句话可以帮大家记忆：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三片叶子不要碰。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要是早点知道就好了。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很痒。我要用燕麦洗冷水澡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还要涂粉色的乳液。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唉！我再也不会走到路外边去了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>